You can also check the deployment status from OpenShift Console.

- Go to Adminstration-> Custom Resource Definition.
  - Search for manageworkspace
  

![image](images/crd.png)      

  - Go to instances tab. Select your project instance.

![image](images/cr.png) 


  - Check status

![image](images/status.png)
